'''克罗莫结构域'''或'''染色質結構域'''（{{lang-en|Chromodomain}}，''<u>chr</u>omatin <u>o</u>rganization <u>mo</u>difier''<ref name="pmid1628830">{{cite journal | author = S Messmer, A Franke, R Paro| title = Analysis of the functional role of the Polycomb chromo domain in Drosophila melanogaster | journal = Genes Dev. | volume = 6 | issue = 7 | pages = 1241–1254 | pmid = 1628830 | doi = 10.1101/gad.6.7.1241 | url =https://archive.org/details/sim_genes-development_1992-07_6_7/page/1241|date=July 1992}}</ref>）是一种由40～50个[[氨基酸|氨基酸]]残基组成的[[蛋白质|蛋白质]][[结构域|结构域]]，往往存在于那些与[[染色质|染色质]]重塑及操控有关的蛋白质里。此结构域不管在植物及动物之中都高度[[保守_(遗传学)|保守]]，且在许多[[基因组|基因组]]（如[[小鼠|小鼠]]）中代表了较大数量的各种蛋白质。许多包含克罗莫结构域的[[基因|基因]]有多种[[可变剪接|可变剪接]]亚型，有些亚型完全把克罗莫结构域当作内含子切除出去<ref name="Tajul">{{cite journal | doi = 10.1101/gr.1015703 | last1 = Tajul-Arifin | first1 = K | last2 = Teasdale | first2 = R | last3 = Ravasi | first3 = T | last4 = Humel | first4 = DA | last5 = Group | first5 = RIKEN GER | last6 = Members | first6 = GSL | last7 = Mattick | first7 = JS. | author-separator =, | author-name-separator= | year = 2003 | title = Identification and Analysis of Chromodomain-Containing Proteins Encoded in the Mouse Transcriptome | url = | journal = Genome Res | volume = 13 | issue = 6B| pages = 1416–1429 | pmid = 12819141 | pmc = 403676 }}</ref>。在[[哺乳动物|哺乳动物]]中，包含克罗莫结构域的蛋白质主要负责涉及到染色质重塑及形成[[异染色质|异染色质]]区域这两方面的[[基因调控|基因调控]]<ref name="Jones">{{cite journal | doi = 10.1002/(SICI)1521-1878(200002)22:2<124::AID-BIES4>3.0.CO;2-E | last1 = Jones | first1 = DO | last2 = Cowell | first2 = IG | last3 = Singh | first3 = PB. | author-separator =, | author-name-separator= | year = 2000 | title = Mammalian chromodomain proteins: their role in genome organisation and expression | url = | journal = Bioessays | volume = 22 | issue = 2| pages = 124–37 | pmid = 10655032 }}</ref>。包含克罗莫结构域的蛋白质亦会结合到[[甲基化|甲基化]][[组蛋白|组蛋白]]上<ref name="Nielsen">{{cite journal | doi = 10.1038/nature722 | last1 = Nielsen | first1 = PR | last2 = Nietlispach | first2 = D | last3 = Mott | first3 = HR | last4 = Callaghan | first4 = J | last5 = Bannister | first5 = A | last6 = Kouzarides | first6 = T | last7 = Murzin | first7 = AG | last8 = Murzina | first8 = NV | last9 = Laue | first9 = ED. ''et al.'' | author-separator =, | author-name-separator= | year = 2002 | title = Structure of the HP1 chromodomain bound to histone H3 methylated at lysine 9 | url = | journal = Nature | volume = 416 | issue = 6876| pages = 103–7 | pmid = 11882902 }}</ref><ref name="Jacobs">{{cite journal | doi = 10.1126/science.1069473 | last1 = Jacobs | first1 = SA | last2 = Khorasanizadeh | first2 = S. | author-separator =, | author-name-separator= | year = 2002 | title = Structure of HP1 chromodomain bound to a lysine 9-methylated histone H3 tail | url = | journal = Science | volume = 295 | issue = 5562| pages = 2080–3 | pmid = 11859155 }}</ref>且存在于[[RNA诱导的转录沉默|RNA诱导的转录沉默]]复合物中<ref name="Verdel">{{cite journal | doi = 10.1126/science.1093686 | last1 = Verdel | first1 = A | last2 = Jia | first2 = S | last3 = Gerber | first3 = S | last4 = Sugiyama | first4 = T | last5 = Gygi | first5 = S | last6 = Grewal | first6 = S | last7 = Moazed | first7 = D | author-separator =, | author-name-separator= | year = 2004 | title = RNAi-Mediated Targeting of Heterochromatin by the RITS Complex | url = | journal = Science | volume = 303 | issue = 5658| pages = 672–6 | pmid = 14704433 | pmc = 3244756 }}</ref>。

